description: Alexa will play a note your request (played on a simulated oboe) to help you tune your instrument.  Currently My Tuning Oboe will only play A, B-Flat, or F.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask My Tuning Oboe to give me an A.
Alexa, ask My Tuning Oboe to play an F
Alexa, ask My Tuning Oboe for a B-Flat
name: My Tuning Oboe
shortDescription: Play a note for tuning an instrument.
